nding that was in escrow, and started using his Platinum Amex card to pay Z=
ero-G=E2=80=99s expenses. Meanwhile, he calculated the amount needed to get=
 the company
through the jet=E2=80=99s next scheduled maintenance program in June 2020.=
=C2=A0

=C2=A0

To make up the shortfall, Gohd decided to pivot to an experience business=
=E2=80=94one poised to benefit from the sort of quirky, devil-may-care spen=
