=C2=A0

=E2=80=9CIt=E2=80=99s not like going up on Blue Origin for a million and a
half bucks for a 10-minute rocket ride, which would scare the shit out of 9=
0 percent of the population,=E2=80=9D Gohd told me, =E2=80=9Cor going up wi=
th [Branson] on a rocket glider [at $600,000 per flight].=E2=80=9D Plus, =
=E2=80=9COur safety record is impeccable. Nobody=E2=80=99s ever been hurt. =
We=E2=80=99ve flown 22,000 people plus.=E2=80=9D After Gohd proved to the F=
=2EA.A. that the air circulating within=
 his jet was purified and filtered, th=
